---
// FTC affiliate disclosure — short form, appears on every page above the footer.
// Long form lives at /disclosure.
---

<aside class="disclosure">
  <p>
    Some links on this page are affiliate links. If you click and buy something,
    Trove Collections may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you. We only
    recommend items we — or someone in our trusted curator circle — have personally
    used and would give as a gift. Editorial integrity is the entire point of this
    site, so we will never feature an item just because we could earn from it.
    <a href="/disclosure">Full disclosure &rarr;</a>
  </p>
</aside>

<style>
  .disclosure {
    background: #F1E9DC;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .disclosure p {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .disclosure a {
    color: var(--accent);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
</style>
